<section
    id="positive-trade"
    class="relative text-[#e7e5e4] font-serif min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-12 md:py-24 border-b border-emerald-900/10"
>
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
        <span class="text-emerald-500/80 text-xs md:text-sm tracking-[0.2em] uppercase block mb-4"
            >III. El Comercio</span
        >
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#e7e5e4] mb-8">El Primer Dinero</h2>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center text-left">
            <div class="space-y-6">
                <p class="text-lg text-[#d6d3d1] leading-relaxed">
                    Antes del oro, fue el grano. El siclo (shekel) original no era una moneda, era
                    una medida de peso de cebada.
                </p>
                <p class="text-base text-[#a8a29e] leading-relaxed">
                    El excedente de trigo permitió el comercio a larga distancia. Conectó tribus
                    aisladas. Llevó obsidiana de Anatolia a Jericó y conchas del Mediterráneo al
                    desierto. El trigo tejió la primera red global de cooperación humana.
                </p>
            </div>

            <div
                class="bg-[#1c1917] p-8 rounded border border-emerald-900/10 flex flex-col items-center justify-center gap-6"
            >
                <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-emerald-500/50">
                    <div
                        class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full border-2 border-current flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            class="w-8 h-8"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M12 3v2.25m6.364.386l-1.591 1.591M21 12h-2.25m-.386 6.364l-1.591-1.591M12 18.75V21m-4.773-4.227l-1.591 1.591M5.25 12H3m4.227-4.773L5.636 5.636M15.75 12a3.75 3.75 0 11-7.5 0 3.75 3.75 0 017.5 0z"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <div class="h-px w-12 bg-current"></div>
                    <div
                        class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full border-2 border-current flex items-center justify-center"
                    >
                        <svg
                            xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                            fill="none"
                            viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                            stroke-width="1.5"
                            stroke="currentColor"
                            class="w-8 h-8"
                        >
                            <path
                                stroke-linecap="round"
                                stroke-linejoin="round"
                                d="M21 11.25v8.25a1.5 1.5 0 01-1.5 1.5H5.25a1.5 1.5 0 01-1.5-1.5v-8.25M12 4.875A2.625 2.625 0 109.375 7.5H12m0-2.625V7.5m0-2.625A2.625 2.625 0 1114.625 7.5H12"
                            ></path>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <p class="text-xs tracking-widest uppercase text-emerald-500/60">
                    Intercambio de Valor
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
